 *              : Renesas M16C Standard Toolchain (V5.45.01)
 * OS           : none
 * H/W Platform : AE1-LF demo board
 * Description  : This is driver of flash.
 * Operation    : none
 * Limitation   : This file can be only used as sample code for AE1-LF.
